    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4567154>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Temporary pool close to BR290 highway (30°22’27”S 53°33’42”W), type locality of Austrolebias paucisquama (above) and detailed image of the vegetation coverage." ;
